{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1636150/extras/_1_\u89c6\u98913.gif?t=1676864991\" /><br>If\u00a0you\u00a0are\u00a0interested\u00a0in\u00a0this\u00a0game,\u00a0please\u00a0add\u00a0it\u00a0to\u00a0your\u00a0wish\u00a0list.<br><br><br><strong>Majestic War Scene</strong><br><br>The game shows players a highly realistic and magnificent war scene. The commander directs navy, army, and air force troops to launch a real battle with the enemy regiments. Each battle supports thousands of units to fight on the same screen, with hundreds of weapons for you to choose .<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1636150/extras/Fight_616x200.gif?t=1676864991\" /><br><br><strong>Establish Decrees</strong><br><br>Formulate appropriate force regulations, flexibly deploy human resource relationships, maintain the motivation and satisfaction of the army, earn the reputation of civilians in every victory, and let your army go to victory under your wise leadership.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1636150/extras/_3_\u89c6\u9891.gif?t=1676864991\" /><br><br><strong>Training The Army</strong><br><br>Training, providing logistics support, building camps, arranging defense, various restrictions and hinder are the key to determine the victory or defeat of the battle. You must weigh the pros and cons and make a careful choice to strike a balance between various factors.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1636150/extras/DailyTraining_616x200.gif?t=1676864991\" /><br><br><strong>Social And Relationships</strong><br><br>As a commander of the army, you need to maintain a good relationship and coordination with your colleagues, and also need to deal with your superior and subordinate relations so that everyone can work together. Every soldier has his own personality. Dealing with the relationship with every soldier will be one of the key factors for your success or failure.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1636150/extras/_5_\u89c6\u9891.gif?t=1676864991\" /><br><br><strong>Be Careful Your Choice</strong><br><br>You should consider each decision you make, because seemingly insignificant decisions may have a great impact on you.  Subordinates trust you and they are willing to devote their life. As their leader, you bear heavy responsibility and all your choices are significant.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1636150/extras/_6_\u89c6\u9891.gif?t=1676864991\" /><br><br><strong>Develop New Technology</strong><br><br>Compared with manpower and resources, war is a contest of science and technology. While developing your own army, you should also look further, look into the future, invest in the development of new technology, and put more sophisticated weapons into the battlefield to help you win.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1636150/extras/CustomWeapon_616x200.gif?t=1676864991\" /><br><br><strong>Vast Map</strong><br><br>North Africa, Middle Myanmar, Europe... Famous battlefields. As the commander of the army, the player needs to collect materials, deploy troops, strategic bombing, deploy defense, and siege and loot on the vast and complex map. You will write your own epic war with your army together.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1636150/extras/BigMap_Gif_616x200.gif?t=1676864991\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Completed 10 R&D","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1636150/4696a96645c74769a7392d02b12f270806a0694d.jpg"},{"name":"Completed 25 R&D","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.co